---terraform
commands to run 
need to connect to provider which is in main tf feom terrafrom website copy pasted
terraform init ---inside you folder to intialize it, download some files like.lock.hcl
terraform plan---(give change state like cloudformation)
terraform apply ---creates the bucket /// or terraform apply --auto-approve (for not hitting yes for change sets)
terraform destroy---destroy it 

--cloudformation
./deploy---will run deploy file


---cdk
first cdk folder
globally install not in folder using---"npm i -g aws-cdk"---creates files in cdk folder
now in lib folder we have our "cdk-stacks.ts" file (main file where we create and amnage everything)
cdk bootstrap--cmd
cdk deploy --cmd
cdk destroy --cmd